dct_title_s: Nijūmanbun no ichi zu Tōbu "So"ryō Saharinshū
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
Set covers northern half of Island.
Based on maps made in 1935 by Red Army General Staff.
Index map and legend in margins.
